{"tid":2330913,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉警察遊樂會停車場擲汽油彈案 三男子被控縱火 明早西九龍法院提堂","createTime":"2020-12-18T11:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T10:35:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"14721f183f5231409de9a6e792ed74e6177196af","tid":2330913,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:05:55.000Z","msg":"警方拘捕3名16歲至23歲的男子，涉嫌與本月初有人向太子警察遊樂會停車場投擲汽油彈有關，將被落案起訴縱火罪，明日早上於西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n西九龍總區重案組總督察陳鈺敏表示，事發於本月1日凌晨，有3人向警察遊樂會停車場投擲多枚汽油彈，一部貨櫃車焚毀，警方分析大量閉路電視片段後，今早於大圍、葵涌及尖沙咀拘捕這3名男子，3人分別為中四學生、藥房職員及無業。<br />\n<br />\n警方又在旺角區一幢大廈，搜出製造汽油彈的原材料，包括電油、泵及啤酒樽。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，當日案發後警方即時拘捕一名男子，經調查後發現他與案無關，而他藏有胡椒噴劑的案件，會繼續由警方跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566060-20201218.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566060-20201218.htm&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=a9e81e6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566060-20201218.htm&h=614a822c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566060-20201218.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ee452e37910006408fdbf1205c1427d170b3fd40","tid":2330913,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ae8eea086ab21d043868751e7839bc8132af7f","tid":2330913,"uid":123138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f4946cbb5aaf8e5c156cde714ee153639293c4","tid":2330913,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-1